description: The dataset includes detailed  information on Medicare FFS claims that underwent CERT medical review for the FY 2014 report period (claims submitted  July 1, 2012 through June 30, 2013.)  These claims were used to calculate the FY 2014 Medicare FFS improper payment rate.
